
Styles archive
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~


Config ROM
~~~~~~~~~~

! <config width="250"
!         height="320">

The optional attributes 'width' and 'height' assign a minimum height and width
to the top-level element in the dialog ROM. The values are given in numbers of
pixels. The default value is 0 for both.


Dialog ROM
~~~~~~~~~~

! <frame>

Renders a box with the frame style given through the styles archive.


! <button>

Renders a box with the button style given through the styles archive.


! <label text="Hallo Welt!">

Renders a line of text given through the 'text' attribute.


! <vbox>

Arranges sub-elements top-down in a column.


! <hbox>

Arranges sub-elements left-to-right in a row.


! <float>

Positions a sub-element in an oversized parent element. By default the
sub-element is positioned in the center of the parent element.


! <cursor name="" style="" at="">
